Our values

Designed for forward-thinking, care-obsessed operators

We believe senior living communities deserve exceptional technology that enables them to provide exceptional care.

Accessible data, actionable insights

An operating strategy is only as good as the data that’s driving it. Our  embedded BI dashboard delivers unmatched visibility and predictive capabilities for resident care, operations, and performance oversight at your communities.

Unquestionably caregiver-friendly

August Health is easy to learn and easy to use. Communities rapidly adopt our platform because every interface and interaction is designed to be efficient, intuitive, and helpful — allowing staff to focus on resident care.

Purpose-built for proactive care

We help operators shift from reactive tactics to proactive care strategies. Built-in intelligence and smarter workflows help you spot trends, address risks earlier, and stay a step ahead of everything from increasing acuity to compliance deadlines.
